		<technology>
			<technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses xml:lang="en">Based on 17.6 kg of sodium persulfate per ton of contaminated soil.</technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses>
			<technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses xml:lang="zh">以每吨污染土壤投放17.6kg过硫酸钠药剂为标准</technologyDescriptionAndIncludedProcesses>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="en">The soil remediation process described is used for in-situ treatment of contaminated soil. Specifically, it involves in-situ chemical oxidation by injection of oxidizing agents as a unit process (single operation). This technique is suitable for addressing organic contaminants in the soil, such as petroleum hydrocarbons, solvents, and pesticides. The process is applied directly in the contaminated area without the need to excavate soil, thus minimizing physical disturbances to the site. It is commonly used in environmental engineering and land rehabilitation projects.</technologicalApplicability>
			<technologicalApplicability xml:lang="zh">描述的土壤修复工艺用于处理受污染土壤的原位治理。具体来说，该过程涉及通过注入氧化剂作为单一操作的原位化学氧化。这项技术适用于处理土壤中的有机污染物，例如石油烃、溶剂和农药。此工艺直接在污染区域内施行，无需挖掘土壤，从而最小化对现场的物理干扰。它通常用于环境工程和土地复垦项目。</technologicalApplicability>
			<referenceToTechnologyFlowDiagrammOrPicture type="source data set" refObjectId="2eb83e92-f5ab-eb7f-0339-62bfceed9af3" uri="../sources/2eb83e92-f5ab-eb7f-0339-62bfceed9af3.xml">
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="en">Imedba4HZot44gxnb7Gc7O8Enfc.png</common:shortDescription>
			</referenceToTechnologyFlowDiagrammOrPicture>
		</technology>
